<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>WVB Engineering | Binnenkort online</title>

    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background: #f7fbff;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px;
        color: white;
      }

      .card {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1280px;
        min-height: 720px;
        background: #282569;
        border-radius: 22px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(60, 120, 170, 0.18);
        padding: 120px 110px;
      }

      .content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        max-width: 540px;
      }

      .label {
        font-size: 22px;
        letter-spacing: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 22px;
      }

      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 22px;
        margin-bottom: 26px;
      }

      .logo-mark {
        width: 130px;
        height: 78px;
        position: relative;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .logo-mark span {
        position: absolute;
        width: 70px;
        height: 38px;
        border-radius: 8px 18px 8px 8px;
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        opacity: 0.95;
      }

      .logo-mark .blue {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6fa7dd, #4668b3);
        left: 5px;
        top: 18px;
      }

      .logo-mark .red {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff1f25, #ff8c6b);
        left: 52px;
        top: 18px;
      }

      .logo-mark .green {
        background: #b9e6ad;
        left: 96px;
        top: 18px;
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
        transform: none;
        border-radius: 8px 18px 8px 8px;
      }

      .brand-text {
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 48px;
        line-height: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
      }

      .body-text {
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.45;
        margin: 0 0 38px;
      }

      .contact {
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.45;
        margin-bottom: 34px;
      }

      .contact strong {
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #6ea4dc;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 21px;
        font-weight: 800;
        padding: 17px 34px;
        border-radius: 9px;
        transition: 0.2s ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: #82b6ea;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .tagline {
        position: absolute;
        right: 92px;
        bottom: 178px;
        z-index: 2;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1.08;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .shape {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        width: 260px;
        height: 165px;
        border-radius: 18px 80px 18px 18px;
        opacity: 0.82;
      }

      .shape.blue {
        right: 360px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6fa7dd, #4668b3);
      }

      .shape.red {
        right: 160px;
        background: #f51f26;
      }

      .shape.green {
        right: -24px;
        background: #b9e6ad;
      }

      .shape::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border-radius: inherit;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        body {
          padding: 14px;
        }

        .card {
          min-height: auto;
          padding: 70px 32px 190px;
        }

        .label {
          font-size: 16px;
          letter-spacing: 6px;
        }

        .brand {
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 14px;
        }

        .logo-mark {
          width: 88px;
          height: 55px;
        }

        .logo-mark span {
          width: 46px;
          height: 28px;
        }

        .logo-mark .red {
          left: 36px;
        }

        .logo-mark .green {
          left: 68px;
          width: 28px;
          height: 28px;
        }

        .brand-text {
          font-size: 34px;
        }

        .body-text,
        .contact {
          font-size: 18px;
        }

        .button {
          font-size: 17px;
          padding: 15px 24px;
        }

        .tagline {
          right: 28px;
          bottom: 92px;
          font-size: 25px;
        }

        .shape {
          height: 105px;
          width: 150px;
        }

        .shape.blue {
          right: 210px;
        }

        .shape.red {
          right: 95px;
        }

        .shape.green {
          right: -30px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="card">
      <section class="content">
        <div class="label">Binnenkort online</div>

        <div class="brand">
          <div class="logo-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="blue"></span>
            <span class="red"></span>
            <span class="green"></span>
          </div>

          <div class="brand-text">
            WVB<br />
            ENGINEERING
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="body-text">
          Wij werken aan een nieuwe website om onze projecten en expertise beter
          te laten zien. Heeft u in de tussentijd een vraag of project?
        </p>

        <div class="contact">
          Neem gerust contact op.<br />
          <strong>E-mail: info@wvbengineering.nl</strong>
        </div>

        <a class="button" href="mailto:info@wvbengineering.nl">
          MAIL ONS DIRECT
        </a>
      </section>

      <div class="tagline">
        WE DESIGN<br />
        WE BUILD<br />
        WE SERVICE
      </div>

      <div class="shape blue"></div>
      <div class="shape red"></div>
      <div class="shape green"></div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
